org.keycloak.federation.ldap.idm.model

Interface IdentityType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AttributedType, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractIdentityType, LDAPUser

    public interface IdentityType
extends AttributedType
    This interface is the base for all identity model objects. It declares a number of properties that must be supported by all identity types, in addition to defining the API for identity attribute management.
    Author:
    Shane Bryzak
